text: The 1932 Ohio gubernatorial election was held on November 8, 1932. Incumbent Democrat George White defeated Republican nominee David Sinton Ingalls with 52.82% of the vote. ==General election== ===Candidates=== Major party candidates *George White, Democratic *David Sinton Ingalls, Republican Other candidates *Joseph Sharts, Socialist *Aaron S. Watkins, Prohibition *John Marshall, Communist *William Woodhouse, Socialist Labor ===Results=== ==References== 1932 Ohio Gubernatorial
title: 1932 Ohio gubernatorial election
